allorsUnifiedGood.name: CONTRAC COBUS 3000
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
- The COBUS is the proven market leader:

- Totally reliable,

- Most economic to operate,

- Competitively priced.

- The airport bus used and trusted around the globe.

- Maximum comfort and extremely short load-unload cycles are due to the 3 extra large doors on each side and the suspension lowering ability of the COBUS for easy embarking and disembarking.
